{"tid":201254,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(dse雞) 考完試想搵關於倉嘅工返","createTime":"2017-04-14T15:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T23:20:42.000Z","uid":2502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f61cfe7b9de574f4c929479e3ec1e89c3a882dc0","tid":201254,"uid":2502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"想問下咁多位巴打 如果我想做倉,係咪去勞工處、搵工網都ok?<br />\n我見網上面好多都只係請fulltime<br />\n另外想問下有冇巴打做過機場嘅倉,聽講好似辛苦過一般嘅倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後想問有冇巴打做緊倉可以介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ea9a040d3ca342f6f306f123df929a6175b702","tid":201254,"uid":29621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"我當年考完DSE返過ZARA倉<br />\nD人都幾nice不過個蛇頭好撚閪<br />\n我返左一排之後有幾日腸胃炎請左2日假<br />\n佢就叫我唔使再返工<br />\n<br />\n利申 : fd介紹"},{"pid":"5761124994a78c45cccc6507d6aebed10d980574","tid":201254,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T15:45:12.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠18先？"},{"pid":"c07e5d296f0f0572c88b8345164a0e1f0d0f8552","tid":201254,"uid":2502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T15:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夠唔夠18先？</blockquote><br />\n唔夠啊 差幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0968136b6d2a29b35ad6135c1fa739f4c11efae","tid":201254,"uid":2502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我當年考完DSE返過ZARA倉<br />\nD人都幾nice不過個蛇頭好撚閪<br />\n我返左一排之後有幾日腸胃炎請左2日假<br />\n佢就叫我唔使再返工<br />\n<br />\n利申 : fd介紹</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下大概有咩做同辛唔辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737f5261c1f16e771920a8913f822d669d1d1616","tid":201254,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"搬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甘唔甘就睇做咩貨 <br />\n手袋 衫褲呢d咪好 我有一排做雪櫃電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw dse岩岩出黎 只要受得氣 比人屌屌下就掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf433188d9ac8f87c26181fc7940947ad424331","tid":201254,"uid":2502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甘唔甘就睇做咩貨 <br />\n手袋 衫褲呢d咪好 我有一排做雪櫃電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw dse岩岩出黎 只要受得氣 比人屌屌下就掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前返學嗰陣都返左2年幾飲食業pt,自問都算捱得下<br />\n巴打有冇咩門路介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381746ec219142d9974bf585df9b2c7208319799","tid":201254,"uid":2502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611937b0e82211bf100ae4c1b991bb3b53148059","tid":201254,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甘唔甘就睇做咩貨 <br />\n手袋 衫褲呢d咪好 我有一排做雪櫃電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw dse岩岩出黎 只要受得氣 比人屌屌下就掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n甘你老母"},{"pid":"fee8d334efe69582070acdbaab712799391f0fb4","tid":201254,"uid":23974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:37:45.000Z","msg":"有冇興趣番下會展"},{"pid":"9e8433fee06a23e4d2cc9cabbcd160add5d27f90","tid":201254,"uid":23974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇興趣番下會展</blockquote><br />\n不過唔係做倉，但都係搬搬抬抬"},{"pid":"86c5bf79ff93085f663441351d6082045ec8f3ed","tid":201254,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy